Key Match Events: Mohamed Bayo scored an early goal for Guinea.
Francois Kamano, Guinea's stand-in captain, received a red card after a VAR review.
Frank Magri scored the equalizer for Cameroon with a header from a Georges-Kevin Nkoudou cross.
Post-Match Reflections: Cameroon were frustrated with their inability to defeat a 10-man Guinea.
The result was seen as ideal for defending champions Senegal in Group C.
